Firefly.
This is a simple game and experiment with the Akihabara game engine where you are a kid wandering around and collecting fireflies. The concept will be expanded in the future.

Game Design and Art by David Frankel
Programming by Quin Kennedy

Music: I Like Sour Cream by mysterylunch
http://www.newgrounds.com/audio/listen/264255
http://mysterylunch.newgrounds.com/

SFX: taken from capman
https://github.com/Akihabara/demo-capman/tree/master/resources/audio
